---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="DonateCrate FAQ"
  description="Frequently asked questions about pricing, pickup cadence, service areas, and how DonateCrate works."
>
  <main class="simple-page">
    <a class="back-link" href="/">Back to home</a>
    <span class="eyebrow">FAQ</span>
    <h1>Common questions before your first pickup.</h1>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <article>
        <h2>How often are pickups?</h2>
        <p>DonateCrate is designed around a monthly pickup rhythm, with account tools for each active cycle.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>What does it cost?</h2>
        <p>Launch pricing is currently $5 per month per household.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>How do I know if I am in the launch area?</h2>
        <p>Use the address search on the homepage. It checks active and planned route availability for your address.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>What if my address is not active yet?</h2>
        <p>Join the waitlist. We use that demand signal to plan where the next route expansion should happen.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
